App workflow :

	- get the url in the index by the domain/controller/method?params logic
	- @see controller index method for more details

Controller logic :

	- load the model with the same name ( e.g. AnunturiController -> Anunturi (model) )

'sql' File logic :

	- copy/paste the v0.1.php file and replace the query with the desired one, then right-click run.



